Name: CM RCS CHECK
checklistText:
CM RCS Monitoring Check

		CM RCS PRPLNT tb (both) - bp/gray (mission need)
		RCS IND sel - CM 1, 2
			CM RCS He TEMP ind - 60°-90°
			Prior to CM RCS activation
				CM RCS He PRESS ind - 4100-4200 psia
				CM RCS MANF PRESS ind - 80-105 psia



		After CM RCS activation
			CM RCS He PRESS ind - stab at 3300-
				3500 psia ≈15 min after activation
			CM RCS MANF PRESS ind - 287-302 psia

Steps.Text: CM RCS PRPLNT tb (both) - bp/gray (mission need)

CM RCS He PRESS ind - 4100-4200 psia
CM RCS MANF PRESS ind - 80-105 psia
